      • addMetaTag

        public static IMetaInfo[] addMetaTag(IMetaInfo[] metaTags,
                     IMetaInfo metaTag)
        Append a IMetaTag to an array of IMetaTag.
        Parameters:
        metaTags - An existing array of meta tags. May be empty but may not be null.
        metaTag - The new meta tag to append to the metaTags array. If null, the metaTags parameter is returned unmodified.
        Returns:
        The new array of meta tags.

      • createGotoDefinitionHelp

        public static MetaTag createGotoDefinitionHelp(IDefinition definition,
                               String file,
                               String pos,
                               boolean ctor)
        Create a new meta tag for either "__go_to_ctor_definition_help" or "__go_to_definition_help".
        Parameters:
        definition - The definition to add the meta data for.
        file - The absolute path of the source file the definition is found in. May be null.
        pos - The position of the definition in the source file. If "-1" no MetaTag is created.
        ctor - True if the definition is for a constructor, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        A new MetaTag. If the pos paramater is "-1", null is returned.
